    2219 [label="SPDXLicense:\nThis license was released: 29 June 2007. This license identifier refers to the\nchoice to use code under GPL-3.0-or-later (i.e., GPL-3.0 or some later version),\nas distinguished from the use of code under GPL-3.0-only. The license notice (as\nseen in the Standard License Header field below) states which of these applies\nto the code in the file. The example in the How to Apply These Terms appendix of\nthe license shows the \"or later\" approach."
